## Commands

When building storefront pages, follow these workflows:
- **generate-page**: Generate a complete Shopify landing page — auto-detects vertical and applies best patterns (uses: storefront-craft, workflow-orchestration, conversion-psychology, page-generation)
- **optimize-page**: Analyze and optimize an existing page for better conversions (uses: conversion-psychology, page-editing, analytics)
- **create-assets**: Generate brand-matched visual assets — search library first, generate if needed (uses: visual-craft, design-enrichment, design-assets)
- **run-experiment**: Set up an A/B test with a variant page and monitor results (uses: conversion-psychology, page-generation, analytics)
